---
title: Moroccan Chicken Sausage Tagine with Dried Apricots & Chickpeas over Basmati Rice
description: For this meal, we’re headed to Morocco with a sweet and savory chicken sausage tagine over basmati rice. This stew-like dish is the definition of hearty and features ingredients like carrots, chickpeas, and tomatoes. After everything gets a quick sauté with warming spices, chicken broth is added to make things as cozy and filling as can be. Dried apricots are sprinkled over top for chewy texture and sweetness, while a creamy sauce is drizzled over everything for just a touch of heat.
